{"tid":746018,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人假扮日本人","createTime":"2018-07-17T08:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T09:21:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c0bc907605ff40dc1cdcf8c75d5678f6e7133d","tid":746018,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180717/20451634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F20451634&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36EaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=434a00d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F20451634&h=89d6596d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180717/20451634</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人假扮日本人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180717/large/e88a10a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180717%2Flarge%2Fe88a10a.jpg&h=e5444755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncatanianews.it新聞截圖<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一對中國男女手持假的日本護照，準備從意大利卡塔尼亞（Catania）機場飛往英國倫敦，被地勤人員當場識破，轉交警察處理，警察後來證實他們使用假護照，將他們扣押，等候審訊。<br />\n<br />\n中國人竟然夠膽假扮日本人？他們大約以為在外國人眼中，所有的黃皮膚黑頭髮亞洲人都一模一樣吧。如果真的這麼想，也未免太「輕敵」。<br />\n<br />\n這幾年中國人大舉湧入歐洲，不論是以富豪身份「振興當地經濟」的，還是以黑勞身份去掠奪當地人工作機會的，一律嘈吵，人未到聲先至，離去後必一地垃圾。歐洲人早就領教夠了。怎麼可能認不出中國人？<br />\n<br />\n中國人的舉止、動靜、氣質與其他亞洲人不一樣，光看背影，就很容易分出日本人、韓國人、中國人。中國人走在街上手臂擺動幅度特別大，最大可能地侵佔空間，稍作留意，不難發現。日本人正好相反，是最大可能地把自己縮到最小，希望不打擾到任何人。日本人氣質優雅嫺靜，泰山崩於頂色不變。中國人凡事必大驚小怪、呼天搶地。<br />\n<br />\n一對中國男女走到地勤面前，突然拿出兩本日本護照，以後會發生甚麼，已經能夠預見。不是護照穿崩，而是他們的模樣穿崩。<br />\n<br />\n有人說，中國人扮日本人，必須先去整容，把臉形改一改。但是就算整了容也沒有用，就算穿一身日本製造的衣物還是沒有用，日本人那種從內至外散發出來的恬淡，中國人永遠模仿不來。  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36EaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=d8598405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n探花的二十四孝父母 (鄧達智)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n人不犯我，我必犯人 (古德明)"},{"pid":"7b80be61bdeadc5313c1443fe78db96c32a55c2b","tid":746018,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b7d7fbb3138b3e9b6d2cc0e29eeb297c1b6468","tid":746018,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"係真 正如強國人都扮唔到香港人"},{"pid":"1676de6fdf86b61bead7be6249d2e0ed715c39e6","tid":746018,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"支泡同源<br />\n真心難認"},{"pid":"89355660a4f2079ce9cfcc5066d1a437162b3b59","tid":746018,"uid":176366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"以為係19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebce04c1853cf4ab4b608118ce02c0abe81b3fe","tid":746018,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b7d7fbb3138b3e9b6d2cc0e29eeb297c1b6468","tid":746018,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"係真 正如強國人都扮唔到香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"其實除左蹲路邊之外都幾接近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eea861f104617ba1f68afa7175c0c00d620d17b","tid":746018,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b7d7fbb3138b3e9b6d2cc0e29eeb297c1b6468","tid":746018,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:00:32.000Z","